output.analysis:
Let's analyze this post according to our criteria:
1. Has CMF: Yes - "CMF: 11240017" is present at the end of the post, indicating this is electoral content.
2. Refers to candidate: Yes - Marcel Ciolacu is mentioned, who is a presidential candidate (Position 3 on the ballot).
3. Addresses wide population: Yes - This is a paid post on Facebook/Instagram with an estimated reach of 3,000-3,999 impressions, clearly intended for mass communication.
4. Electoral objective: Yes - While the post appears to be about Schengen accession, it prominently features Marcel Ciolacu's achievements as Prime Minister, highlighting his leadership capabilities during a presidential campaign period.
5. Journalism: No - This is not journalistic content but rather a promotional message highlighting the achievements of a specific candidate.
6. Personal opinion: No - This is an official party communication (PSD Dolj) promoting their candidate's achievements.
The timing of this post (November 22, 2024) and its continuation beyond the campaign period makes it problematic under Article 55 t), as it constitutes ongoing electoral propaganda after the conclusion of the official campaign period.

conclusion.electoral-propaganda-analysis: This constitutes electoral propaganda because: - It has an official CMF number - It promotes a presidential candidate's achievements - It's paid advertising reaching a wide audience - It's published by an official party channel (PSD Dolj) - It continues beyond the campaign period
conclusion.message-for-police: PSD Dolj, pentru incalcarea articolului 55 t) din Legea 370/2004, prin promovarea unui material de propagandă electorală (ID postare Facebook: 1104185277756075) după încheierea perioadei de campanie electorală. Materialul, publicat și promovat după ora 18:00 pe 23.11.2024, prezintă realizările candidatului ION-MARCEL CIOLACU, fiind marcat cu cod CMF 11240017, constituind astfel propagandă electorală explicită. Postarea este sponsorizată și distribuită pe Facebook și Instagram, având un impact estimat între 3.000 și 3.999 de afișări, reprezentând o încercare clară de influențare a votului în perioada în care propaganda electorală este interzisă prin lege.
